      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in breathtaking, like-new condition\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh car smell and looks like it just stepped out of a showroom. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept tucked away in a garage, so it\u2019s sparkling inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
