    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, positive engagement, feeding power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Every suspension bushing and damper remains within factory tolerances, preserving the legendary handling kinematics of the M-division. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a pristine interior, this is a turnkey example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
