      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, preserved in absolute showroom condition. This car features a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-like paint clarity and zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks. The interior remains pristine, featuring supple, unscuffed leather, original floor mats in 'out-of-the-box' condition, and that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, and the engine bay is spotless. From the tight, responsive handling to the seamless operation of every electronic feature, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a piece of automotive perfection that has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one.",
